This is a set of Frequently Asked Questions for Chinese-speaking LaTeX users.

The document was written by LingYun Wu. Most questions were collected on the bbs.ctex.org forum, and answered elaborately by the author.

If you are interested in the process of development you may observe

    http://code.google.com/p/ctex-doc/updates/list

Report feedback in the Issues section of ctex-doc project,
or in http://bbs.ctex.org forum.
